item.title: Help with members
item.dc:creator: @kihomura Kihomura
item.description:
@kihomura wrote:

Like, member items?

Well, just delete the requirement.

It should be with your other stat requirements, or whatever.

Or if this a question about like an object that needs membership, go look for the object’s case, and delete the membership requirements from it.
